ingredient_list: Lasagna Noodles;Ground Beef;Ricotta Cheese;Mozzarella Cheese;Tomato Sauce;Parmesan Cheese;Egg;Onion;Garlic;Italian Seasoning
step_descriptions: Boil lasagna noodles until al dente;Brown ground beef with onion and garlic;Mix ricotta cheese, egg, and parmesan cheese;Layer noodles, meat sauce, ricotta mixture, and mozzarella cheese in a baking dish;Bake in preheated oven until bubbly and golden brown;Let cool for 10 minutes before serving
